  "title": "poc: fully managed InstantSearch with custom element",
  "body": "If we choose to bundle a special version of InstantSearch which would just read a static configuration and instantiate itself, this would be one way to specify where blocks should render.\r\n\r\nThis solution uses a custom element called `ais-block` which can be placed anywhere at anytime, regardless of the framework used.",
